name: Spice Mines Of Kessel (V)
Lore: 'Captives sent to the Kessel spice mines spend the rest of their lives digging for glitterstim, a spice sold throughout the galaxy by smugglers and crime lords.',
Text: 'Deploy on Kessel. While your Star Destroyer here, opponent may not play Interrupts from their Lost Pile. If opponent just forfeited a character here, may place this Effect in Lost Pile to retrieve Force equal to that character''s forfeit. (Immune to Alter.)',
